PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1780423900
OL,3,CChannel Islands see record-breaking
OL,4,Ctemperatures in May
OL,6,FOur sea temperature was also warmer
OL,7,Fthan any May on record, with an
OL,8,Faverage temperature of 14.0C.
OL,10,FThe most recent period of prolonged
OL,11,Fhigh temperatures came last year, when
OL,12,Ftemperatures exceeded 30.0C for four
OL,13,Fconsecutive days.
OL,15,FThe maximum in that period was 33.0C.
OL,26,@pD@\OXtD@[OXwD@dOX
